title: Argonne (CDP), Wisconsin
content:
Argonne is an unincorporated census-designated place in the town of Argonne, Forest County, Wisconsin, United States. Argonne is located at the junction of Wisconsin Highway 32 and Wisconsin Highway 55 6 miles (9.7Â km) north of Crandon. Argonne has a post office with ZIP code 54511.[3] The community was established in 1888.[2] As of the 2020 census, its population was 135, down from 160 at the 2010 census.[4]
